data.description:
Welcome to your dream home nestled in the heart of Edmond School district! Situated on a spacious half-acre lot, this stunning residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and luxury living. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a grand entryway that sets the tone for the elegance found throughout the home. 
Assumable loan 
The inviting living room beckons with its warm ambiance, centered around a charming  fireplace, creating a cozy haven for relaxation and entertaining. With three generously sized bedrooms and a full bathroom, there's ample space for family and guests to feel right at home. The luxurious master suite is a sanctuary of indulgence, featuring a spa-like master bathroom complete with his & her vanities, a luxurious walk-in shower, and a spacious walk-in closet, offering a private retreat for unwinding after a long day.
Entertainment abounds in the oversized bonus room, ideal for hosting gatherings, creating a media room, or enjoying a game of pool. Adjacent to the bonus room, a convenient half bath adds to the home's functionality and appeal.

Step outside to discover the enchanting backyard oasis, complete with a covered patio perfect for al fresco dining and relaxation, overlooking the lush landscape that backs up to the serene walking trail, providing a picturesque backdrop for outdoor enjoyment and recreation.
Located in a desirable neighborhood boasting an array of amenities including a sparkling pool, park, sand volleyball court, basketball court, and baseball field, there's no shortage of opportunities for fun and leisure right at your doorstep.
Don't miss your chance to call this exquisite residence your own. Schedule your private showing today and experience the epitome of luxurious living in Edmond!
